  "instructions": [
    "In a large saucepan, heat the vegetable oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and sauté for another minute.",
    "Add the evaporated milk and chicken broth, whisking continuously to prevent lumps.",
    "Add the rice flour and whisk until smooth.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in salt and pepper to taste.",
